cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CR, cs.DS 

This paper deals with analyzing and understanding a workload of SQL queries, which is a core aspect of database systems (cs.DB). The paper also involves feature extraction and sequence analysis, which are common techniques in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the detection of coherent explorations, which can be related to anomaly detection (cs.CR) and pattern recognition (cs.DS).
